Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.10,0:02:15.31,BG-opJ,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Oh, where are you now? Have you gone away?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.33,0:02:19.40,BG-opJ,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Here now, is it just a lookalike?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.42,0:02:22.91,BG-opJ,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}All of the world is slowly changing
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.92,0:02:27.12,BG-opJ,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}In a way I cannot see from here
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.14,0:02:34.10,BG-opJ,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}昨日見た夢では　誰かに呼ばれていた
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.70,0:02:43.80,BG-opJ,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}振り向けばそこには　消えもせず居座った幻
